   - Split 2: "How are you today?" â†’ 00:00:01,500 â†’ 00:00:06,000 (based on actual audio)
   Example (Japanese): Original segment 00:00:00,000 â†’ 00:00:05,000, text "ä»Šæ—¥ã¯ã„ã„å¤©æ°—ã§ã™ã­ã€‚æ•£æ­©ã«è¡Œãã¾ã—ã‚‡ã†ã€‚"
   - If speaker says "ä»Šæ—¥ã¯ã„ã„å¤©æ°—ã§ã™ã­ã€‚" slowly (3s), then quickly says the rest:
